description: Curando Nordic AB operates as a holistic concept company in healthcare. The company is headquartered in Lund, Skane. The company went IPO on 2016-12-22. The firm operates as a provider of information technology (IT) tools integrated into medical services. The firm offers software as a service (SaaS), customer care as a service (CcaaS) and healthcare as a service (HaaS), as well as other IT platform solutions. The firm operates such websites as Agilit.se, Lakartid.nu, Sakravard.nu, Friskapajobbet.se, among others. The firm is focused on provision of digital health and safety services to corporate clients. The company offers occupational health services and other customized solutions. The firm provides Web portal that collects digital applications regarding work environment.
